      <title>银行的目标是下周出售86.5亿欧元的赛诺菲买断债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/banks-aim-to-sell-8-65-billion-sanofi-buyout-debt-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[银行正准备卸载86.5亿欧元（95亿美元）的债务套餐支持Clayton Dubilier＆amp;赖斯购买了赛诺菲SA的消费者健康部门的股份。]]></description>
