    <item>
      <title>法国经济因贸易疑问和政治不稳定而放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/french-economy-slowed-by-trade-doubts-and-political-instability</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该国统计局说，法国的经济陷入了缓慢的增长，这是由于对全球贸易战的担忧以及政治危机对公共支出的影响所压制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/french-economy-slowed-by-trade-doubts-and-political-instability</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳试图控制可可委员会20亿美元的债务堆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/ghana-seeks-to-rein-in-cocoa-board-s-2-billion-debt-pile</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳四面楚歌的可可委员会已经开始对其320亿辆塞迪斯（20亿美元）债务堆的审查，新的首席执行官发誓要兑现其资产负债表，以更好地支持生产商，并在可可的产量下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/ghana-seeks-to-rein-in-cocoa-board-s-2-billion-debt-pile</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 15:52:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
